  <description type="morphology">Plants 3–4 dm. Leaf blade linear, 3–8(–10) × 0.2–0.4(–0.6) cm, thinly to moderately tomentose abaxially, margins often slightly revolute. Involucres 2–3 mm. Perianths white or yellow.</description>
  <description type="phenology">Flowering Jul-Oct.</description>
  <description type="habitat">Red, gypsophilous clay flats and slopes, saltbush, blackbrush, and sagebrush communities;</description>
